name: KOMA DREAMLAND #3
description:
Safrie Effendi's Koma Dreamland Series (3 of 3 ) is the 1st work 

that he created for the NFT platform. 

This work is a Hand-Drawn_Mix-Media_and Digital Collage_ 1000 x 

1600 Pixels_ 2021. 

By far this series is released only 27 edition on each.

Koma Dreamland is all about the life we think and imagine in our 

subconsciousness.

Where the realm dreamy world is to wish to become reality, and 

some people could make it into reality. 

90% of our life is driven by our deep subconsciousness, the 10% 

is the consciousness.

Therefore during this adult life is way better if we could dig 

and manifest more of our subconsciousness.

In order to grow and open up our imagination wide open. 

This is one of the world that we could become anybody or anything 

we wish and desire for.

A collage of images on this series  is a narration that replacing 

words and feelings and that's how Safrie Effendi tries to convey 

his response  to his Koma Dreamland.. Enjoy.
